summary: lycan saved game lev 1 after escaping Helgen.  Imperiel Female Pretty, in a bad mood because the Imperiels wanted to cut off her head.
descriptionHtml:
lycan saved game lev 1
I made this mod for myself, because i was having issues starting over. The game kept crashing when i tried to change from male to female at the beginning.  First I took off all my mods except Apachii hair. Then i made her, saved her after Helgen. Just a plain save game i can fall back on later if needed.
author: Lycanheart
